 # State machine (state.json 'status' field):
 #   active    → normal monitoring, check PR / restart / escalate
 #   pr_open   → PR is open, check CI, notify when green
+#   planning       → Mordecai is generating the plan (agent running)
+#   awaiting_approval → plan posted to Discord, waiting for Josh's reaction
+#   correcting     → Josh reacted ✏️, Zev asked clarifying questions, waiting for answers
+#   implementing   → approved, Mordecai is coding
 #   done      → finished, state file deleted on next run
 #   escalated → max restarts hit, manual intervention needed

